<p>The goal of HotelWherever is to give the consumer the ability to put the hotel decision before the location and flight decision.  We believe that a large part of the vacation experience is to enjoy your favorite hotels around the globe.

<p>For the last minute traveler - we also offer the option to search for those hotels by weather forecasts.  We know nothing ruins a great weekend getaway than a cold rainy day.

<p>Finally, we only choose the best hotels (at least 4 stars) to ensure you are getting finest hotels the world has to offer.</p>

